Amcast Industrial Corp said itcompleted the sale of its Newman Division to NewmanManufacturing Inc, a new company formed by Newman's employees.    The sale price was not disclosed.    Amcast said Newman's Kendallville, Indiana plant is one ofthe country's largest producers of gray iron castings for theautomotive and commercial air conditioning and refrigerationindustries. It said the plant employs 300 people.    Amcast said it decided to sell the division to move out ofthe gray iron castings business. Reuter&#3;